<template>
    <v-date-picker id="datePicker" @click="emitToParent()" v-model='range' :mode='mode' :input-debounce='500'></v-date-picker>
</template>

<script>
import Vue from 'vue';
import DatePicker from 'v-calendar/lib/components/date-picker.umd'
Vue.component('v-date-picker', DatePicker)
export default {
  name: 'DatePicker',
  props: ['start','end'],
  data: function() {
    return{
      mode: 'range',
        range:{
            start: new Date(2018, 0, 16),// Jan 16th, 2018
            end: new Date(2018, 0, 19)    // Jan 19th, 2018
          }
    }
  },
  methods: {
            emitToParent: function() {
                console.log(this.range)
            this.$emit('childToParent', this.range)
        }
    }
}
</script>


<style>
  #datePicker{
    width: 60vw;
    margin: 1vw;
  }
</style>
